{
  "stem": "11957.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't-- I-- I was not afraid of being killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because all my family was killed already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have nothing to live for.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was not afraid of being killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'43.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So basically, until liberation, you were doing this kind of work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once a week, you'd figure out where to blow up a train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At least once a week we-- we'd pick a target.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we-- we go out to that area and scout it out, which way was the best way to approach it and where-- where-- which area to blow it up.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the time they-- they caught on, we were far away from that area because we used to change camps very often.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About every three or four days, we used to change camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have four minutes left on this tape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we picked areas where-- where water was close by and where we-- we wouldn't be spotted from the air.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we picked areas like that where it was water close by.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "200.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody had a job to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yours was blowing up the trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To assemble food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had-- we had to spot-- spot it out where-- where we could get some food for 200 people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ammunitions.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 20 carloads.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
